{"tid":836752,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本通入 名古屋交通一問 感激!","createTime":"2018-09-26T01:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T06:04:39.000Z","uid":176893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0c806a02da2c3e08cbdc76ad77ad7b2ca9006dc3","tid":836752,"uid":176893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"小弟11月出發去名古屋 有無人知由高山去立山 白川鄉 上高地 等等近郊  有無 d pass係好抵玩 見到濃飛巴士單程好貴（仲要預早bk). 有個 5-day pass 又貴又用唔著咁多日<br />\n<br />\n另外 有無巴打絲打知 11月中 呢堆地方係睇楓葉/雪景定乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bbe7b6cfd4f18b0c88c06c40e2587e1e06b36a","tid":836752,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:19:47.000Z","msg":"立山黑部7日周遊券，JR站有售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b71ef99453fa0420b7d5c36ab0c50158d2d21b","tid":836752,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03bbe7b6cfd4f18b0c88c06c40e2587e1e06b36a","tid":836752,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:19:47.000Z","msg":"立山黑部7日周遊券，JR站有售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"5日同8日都有聽過<br />\n7日係咩黎？"},{"pid":"2caa3f8902917f29373f2ed4de1e5150272d6102","tid":836752,"uid":176893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03bbe7b6cfd4f18b0c88c06c40e2587e1e06b36a","tid":836752,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:19:47.000Z","msg":"立山黑部7日周遊券，JR站有售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:15:35.000Z","msg":"但我去得5日  我見呢張券好似包去幾個地方 我唔會去哂 有d佢又包唔哂 所以not a good option <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ba48356